## Window mode (prefix: Ctrl-w)
Switch to next window|w / Ctrl-w
Vertical right split|v / Ctrl-v
Horizontal bottom split|s / Ctrl-s
Go to files in selection in horizontal splits|f
Go to files in selection in vertical splits|F
Move to left split|h / Ctrl-h / Left
Move to split below|j / Ctrl-j / Down
Move to split above|k / Ctrl-k / Up
Move to right split|l / Ctrl-l / Right
Close current window|q / Ctrl-q
Only keep current window, close others|o / Ctrl-o
Swap window to the left|H
Swap window downwards|J
Swap window upwards|K
Swap window to the right|L
